 Burna boy and Wizkid have once again hit the spotlight as they have been nominated for the Black Entertainment (BET) Awards, 2021. The talented singers got nominated in the Best International Act category on May 27, 2021. Other nominees in the category include French singers, Aya Nakamura and Youssoupha; Tanzanian superstar, Diamond Platnumz; Brazilian act, Emicida. Burna Boy has won in the last two years. Before then, Wizkid won the award in 2012, when the category had two divisions for Africa and the UK.